The "If I Have Time" List:
Implement a crafting system (a bit in between on this one).
Add entities.
Use “better” hitboxes for certain entities e.g. Oriented Bounding Boxes.
(instead of current Axis Aligned Bounding Boxes used for the player)


Layers: Layer 1 Layer 2 Layer 3

If you are on layer 1 you can only stand on the red bordered(for visual representation) blocks.
The player hitbox can not physically interact with a layer they’re not occupying.

When you press a key (e.g. E or Q) you can switch to another layer
(only if the space on the target layer is of air).
